== Tutlayt ==
{{Imgradn sis itealqn|Imgradn=[[Taclḥit|Tutlayt Taclḥit]]}}
'''Taclḥit''' ( s [[tifinaɣ]] : ⵜⴰⵛⵍⵃⵉⵜ nɣd ⵜⴰⵙⵓⵙⵉⵜ ) tga yat [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tutlayt tamaziɣt]] illan ɣ tamazirt n lmɣrib, middn li sis isawaln gan Iclḥiyn. nttat ad igan tutlayt tamaziɣt tamzwarut ɣ wuṭṭun n imssiwln d tiriwt n udɣar arakal nna tumẓ, llan uggar gr 8 ar 10 id mlyun ar sis sawaln. 

Tettuysawal Tclḥiyt ɣ [[Sus]], [[Iḥaḥan]], [[Lḥuz]] d kra n tsgg°in yaḍnin tn d iwalan. Tumẓ tutlayt taclḥit zɣ [[Taṣṣurt]] ɣ ugafa ar Agʷlmim ɣ unẓul ar [[Warzazat]] ɣ ugmuḍ. Macc ar tt inn nttafa tlla ula ɣ timdinin mqqurnin n lmɣrib zun d [[Tigmmi Tumlilt]] ( Kaẓa ), d [[Rrbaṭ|Rṛbaḍ]] d Sla.

Tkattin taclḥit ar tt taran s uskkil aɛrab, ilin tugt n warratn iclḥiyn s uskkil aɛrab. Ɣ isggʷasn ad ggʷranin issffɣ [[Asinag ageldan n tussna tamaziɣt|usinag agldan n tussna tamaziɣt]] anaw amaynu n [[tifinaɣ]] ar as tinin [[Tifinaɣ|-{Neo-Tifinaɣ}-]] ntta ɣila a s tt ttaran willi as ssnin. Mac askkil alatini nttan ad akk iggutn slawan ɣ lWeb.

Taclḥit kcmn tt tguriwin tiɛṛabin macc nttat ad igan tutlayt tamaziɣt nna idrus is as kcmt iwaliwn iɛrabn, urd zund [[taqbaylit]] d [[tarifit]] d tutlayin timaziɣin yaḍnin, nẓḍar ad nini mas d nttat ad igan tutlayt tamaziɣt nna akkʷ iṭṭafn uṭṭun imqqurn n iwaliwn iẓɣurann ɣ tmaziɣt, zun d amdya d izwiln nna illan sul ɣ wawal aclḥi ar ass-a. Ɣaynn ad yujjan [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] yaḍnin ad tn asin zɣ taclḥit afad ad tn skcmn s wawal nnsn.

